     CSR         ESB100    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * SET FIELD                                          *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB110    BEGSR
      *
     C                     CLEARBI
     C                     CLEARTI
     C                     CLEARAJ
      *
     C                     SETON                     414243
     C                     SETON                     444546
     C                     SETON                     474849
     C                     SETON                     505152
