     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           *IN05     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVE '99'      DSPSW   2
     C                     MOVE '05'      PCMD
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     CSR         ESB210    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * CHECK                                              *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB400    BEGSR
      *
     C                     Z-ADD1         X
     C                     CLEARTI
